<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>리뷰 · k-ant-daily</title>
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ base_url }}/review.html">
<style>
{% include '_theme.css.j2' %}
  body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--fg);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; }
  main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 20px 64px; }
  h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
  nav { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  nav a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }
  header time { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .hint { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 20px; }
  .empty { background: var(--card); border: 1px dashed var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
           padding: 24px; text-align: center; color: var(--muted); }

  .day-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .day-list li {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto auto; gap: 10px;
    align-items: baseline; padding: 10px 14px;
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .day-list .dt { font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .day-list .score { color: var(--muted); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .day-list .score strong { color: var(--fg); }
  .day-list .rate {
    font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--neu-bg); color: var(--neu);
  }
  .day-list .rate.good { background: var(--pos-bg); color: var(--pos); }
  .day-list .rate.ok   { background: var(--partial-bg); color: var(--partial); }
  .day-list .rate.bad  { background: var(--neg-bg); color: var(--neg); }
  .day-list .retro-link {
    color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .day-list .retro-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .day-list .no-retro { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; }

  footer { margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <header>
    <nav><a href="index.html">← 오늘자</a> · <a href="archive.html">📋 예측</a> · <a href="accuracy.html">📊 통계</a></nav>
    <h1>🎓 리뷰</h1>
    <time>생성 {{ generated_at_display }} KST · {{ records|length }}일 누적</time>
  </header>

  {% if not records %}
  <section class="empty">
    아직 검증된 일자가 없습니다. 평일 저녁 20:10 NXT 마감 후 리뷰가 발행되면 여기에 쌓입니다.
  </section>
  {% else %}

  <p class="hint">일별 회고 · 그날의 예측 vs 실제 · 무엇이 맞았고 무엇이 빗나갔는지</p>

  <ul class="day-list">
    {% for r in records | reverse %}
    {% set rate_pct = (r.hit_rate * 100) | round(0) | int %}
    {% set rate_cls = 'good' if rate_pct >= 60 else ('ok' if rate_pct >= 40 else 'bad') %}
    <li>
      <span class="dt">{{ r.date }}</span>
      <span class="score">
        <strong>{{ r.hits }}</strong> · {{ r.partial }} · {{ r.misses }} / {{ r.total }}건
      </span>
      <span class="rate {{ rate_cls }}">{{ rate_pct }}%</span>
      {% if r.has_retro %}
      <a class="retro-link" href="accuracy/{{ r.date }}.html">🔍 회고 →</a>
      {% else %}
      <span class="no-retro">회고 없음</span>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>

  {% endif %}

  <footer>k-ant-daily · <a href="https://github.com/yummyummyummy/k-ant-daily" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></footer>
</main>
</body>
</html>
